content:
Can you identify the programming language that does not belong with the others in the group based on its unique features and characteristics? 
Here are the programming languages:
- Java
- Python
- C++
- HTML
Using your programming expertise and knowledge, can you identify the language that doesn't fit in and explain why?
To assist you in your analysis, here is an HTML page that contains some code snippets for each language:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Programming Languages</title>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>Programming Languages</h1>
	<h2>Java</h2>
	<pre><code>
	public class HelloWorld {
		public static void main(String[] args) {
			System.out.println("Hello, world!");
		}
	}
	</code></pre>
	<h2>Python</h2>
	<pre><code>
	print("Hello, world!")
	</code></pre>
	<h2>C++</h2>
	<pre><code>
	#include <iostream>
	using namespace std;
	int main() {
		cout << "Hello, world!" << endl;
		return 0;
	}
	</code></pre>
	<h2>HTML</h2>
	<pre><code>
	&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
	&lt;html&gt;
	&lt;head&gt;
		&lt;title&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/title&gt;
	&lt;/head&gt;
	&lt;body&gt;
		&lt;h1&gt;Hello, world!&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;/body&gt;
	&lt;/html&gt;
	</code></pre>
</body>
</html>
```
